data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. What a GREAT price!!  NO HOA!!  NO flood insurance!!  Close to BEACHES!!  Are you an outdoor enthusiast who loves to go the beaches, spend time in the garage, ride bikes/motorcycles, go for a jog?  Or just get messy?  Then you will LOVE the outdoor bathroom in the garage!!  Drive right up... shower... and enter the home clean as a whistle!!  The OPEN floor plan boasts a bright and airy ambiance that seamlessly connects living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for entertaining and everyday living.  Recently REMODELED with NEW backsplash, NEW countertops, and a NEW modern faucet, the kitchen ensures a DELIGHTFUL cooking experience. The home also has a dedicated OFFICE space or BONUS room, perfect for those who work from home or need an extra living space.  Each bedroom is a COZY retreat and is complemented with REMODELED bathrooms that blend functionality with style.  Step thru the SLIDERS to the lovely FENCED backyard that is an OASIS of relaxation. It's perfect for enjoying the beautiful weather, with a POOL, an inviting DECK, and a cozy FIREPIT, offering a private escape or a wonderful spot for gatherings.  You also have a a screened in LANAI that is a PEACEFUL escape for reading a book or outdoor meal. Enjoy the comfort of a widened driveway for EXTRA parking for family and guests, NEW interior/exterior paint, NEW windows and NEW doors ENHANCE the energy efficiency and aesthetics of the home.  NEW water heater, UPDATED electrical system, AC Unit Carrier 2015, Roof 2016, ensuring a move-in ready experience.  A dream for hobbyists or DIY enthusiasts, the SPACIOUS garage includes a WORKSHOP area and provides ample space for vehicle and storage.  Whether you're basking in the comfort of your OPEN-PLAN living area, enjoying the outdoors in your personal FENCED in BACKYARD PARADISE, or exploring the nearby GULF, this home is sure to provide a peaceful and fulfilling living experience.  It is not just a place to live, but a space to love, grow, and create lasting memories. SEE!!  MAKE AN OFFER!!  and get ready to ENJOY!!
